WEBVTT

00:11.075 --> 00:12.515
Embrace your dreams.

00:14.840 --> 00:16.150
If you want to be a hero.

00:18.750 --> 00:20.450
You need to have dreams.

00:23.350 --> 00:23.880
Thank you.

00:29.625 --> 00:30.530
I won't forget.

00:50.630 --> 00:51.150
Good night...

00:59.190 --> 00:59.600
...Zack.

01:18.795 --> 01:19.510
That girl,...

01:21.445 --> 01:25.085
...she said that the sky... frightened her.

01:31.845 --> 01:35.125
That looks so... liberating.

01:41.635 --> 01:42.735
Those wings,...

01:45.305 --> 01:46.435
...I want them too.

02:06.620 --> 02:10.265
It feels... good.

02:21.875 --> 02:24.375
If you see Aerith, say hi for me.

02:39.290 --> 02:44.530
Hey, would you say I became a hero?

